1
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:05,080
This room is all yours.

2
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:07,840
It used to be my dad's office.

3
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:09,760
But he doesn't come around anymore.

4
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,560
The furniture is still in great shape.

5
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:12,920
Right.

6
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:16,160
And feel free to use the TV, too.

7
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:18,480
Sure.

8
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:20,600
Hey.

9
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:22,680
Can you try talking like a normal person?

10
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:25,680
What's the point of that?

11
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,280
Living with you is going to be impossible.

12
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,640
I'm telling my mom to kick you out.

13
00:00:34,680 --> 00:00:35,920
Which one is your room?

14
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:41,640
Don't touch that!

15
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:42,920
Give it back!

16
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:44,400
I said give it back!

17
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:55,240
Who would've thought the school's golden boy was into this?

18
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,480
You wouldn't...

19
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,880
You're not going to tell everyone at school, are you?

20
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,560
If you don't want me to spill the beans...

21
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:04,600
Stop it!

22
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,480
Call me big brother!

23
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,760
Fine, fine.

24
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,760
I'm just messing with you.

25
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,480
I'll be moving out after graduation anyway.

26
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,240
Let's just keep our distance until then.

27
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,240
Deal?

28
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,880
This guy...

29
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:28,000
He's a completely different person than he is at school.
